.B \-f
E 4
E 2
makes a "field" for the worm(s) to eat;
D 2
.B -trail
E 2
I 2
D 4
.B \-trail
E 4
I 4
.B \-t
E 4
E 2
causes each worm to leave a trail behind it.  You can figure
out the rest by yourself.
